    dc:description "FIGURE 12. CT scan images of selected bones. A, Ventrolateral view of lower jaw of Notoglanidium maculatum. B, Lateral view of suspensorium of N. akiri. C, Lateral view of cleithrum of N. akiri. Anterior to left, not to scale. o-den, os dentale; ohyom, os hyomandibulare; o-mpt, metapterygoideum; o-pop, os preoperculare; o-q, os quadratum; o-ar, os anguloarticuloretroarticulare; pr-a, anterior process; pr-cor, coronoid process; pr-hum, humeral process; pr-hyom, anterodorsal hyomandibular process; pr-pd, posterodorsal process." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221681/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

